1. The ArcGIS ______ brings together all the geographic information in your ArcGIS platform and shares it throughout your organization.
    a. Enterprise portal
    b. online account
    c. data repository
    d. software package

2. ArcGIS Data Store is an application that lets you easily configure data storage for the hosting server used with your portal. Which of the following is not one of the 3 types of data stores?
    a. Code snippet data store
    b. Relational data store
    c. Tile cache data store
    d. Spatiotemporal big data store

3. What component of ArcGIS Enterprise allows you to provide a single endpoint that distributes incoming requests to the ArcGIS Server machines in your site.
    a. Web Adapter
    b. Data Store
    c. Portal
    d. Map Viewer